<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>偵錯頁面</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: monospace; background: #222; color: #eee; padding: 2rem; }
    h1 { color: #f90; }
    ul { border: 1px solid #555; padding: 1rem; }
    li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>偵錯: 檢查 collections.tagList</h1>
  <p>這個集合裡面有 {{ collections.tagList | length }} 個項目。</p>
  
  {% if collections.tagList and collections.tagList.length > 0 %}
    <h2>項目列表：</h2>
    <ul>
      {% for tag in collections.tagList %}
        <li>{{ tag }}</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  {% else %}
    <p style="color: #f44;"><strong>錯誤：`collections.tagList` 是空的！</strong></p>
    <p>這代表問題出在 `.eleventy.js` 的設定，或是 `posts/*.json` 檔案中沒有正確的 `tags` 陣列。</p>
  {% endif %}
</body>
</html>
